# Build intermediates — useful for reproducibility but should not clutter
# the deployable repo root. Phase 10 of the /generate-fdi-draft skill
# decides between (a) moving these under .build/ for tracked-but-tucked
# storage, or (b) ignoring them outright (this file's default).
#
# If you want reproducibility tracking, comment out the lines below
# and instead `git mv` these to a .build/ subdirectory.

webset-spec.json
webset-response.json
founder-pick-research.json
lovelace-contacts.json
sumble-jobs.json
curated-10-list.json

# Local plumbing
.build/
node_modules/
*.tmp.json
*.swp
.DS_Store

# Per-build derived files
*-extracted.txt
